The framework should  automate end-to-end test scenarios across the following functional areas:

●  User login, registration, and logout
● Product search and detail verification
● Shopping cart – add and remove items
● Form validations – empty fields and invalid inputs

Key modules available for testing:

 ● Auth – Register, Login, Logout
 ● Products – Search, Browse by category, View product details
 ● Cart – Add, Remove items
 ● Checkout – Address, Payment, Order confirmation